headline: Tecnotree Included as a Representative Provider in Gartner速 Innovation Insight: AI SOC Agents Accelerate CSP SecOps Transformation
summary: ESPOO, Finland, December 31, 2025--Tecnotree, a global digital platform and services provider for communications service providers (CSPs), today announced that it has been referenced as a Representative Provider alongside Google, Anthropic, Dropzone AI, DRUID, Palo Alto Networks, and Pegasystems in the Gartner速 Innovation Insight: "AI SOC Agents Accelerate CSP SecOps Transformation," published in December 2025.
